/*********************************************************************/
/*                 TRANSFER MEMORY TO ZYNQ PL (MM2S)                 */
/*                 AND FROM ZYNQ PL TO MEMORY (S2MM)                 */
/*                                                                   */
/*            THIS C-CODE IS AUTOGENERATED BY gen-c.xslt             */
/*      COMPILE: gcc -Wall -o zynq-axi-dma-sg zynq-axi-dma-sg.c      */
